description.undefined:
The OMICRON ontology aims to represent all the necessary knowledge to support a Road Digitial Twin Information approach.

The OMICRON ontology has been developed as part of the OMICRON project which has received funding from the European Unionâ€™s Horizon 2020 research and innovation programme under grant agreement no. 955269.
